platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love that Cash App freed us from personal checks and IOUs. But we get really excited about Boosts: instant discounts when using your Cash Card. No matter if you swipe your physical Cash Card or tap to pay with Apple Pay, Boosts give you coupon-like perks just for spending money at restaurants, coffee shops, and popular stores.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Easily buy stocks and crypto, track their performance, and cash out in this trusted app.
